OL,3,CTesco apologises after accidentally
OL,4,Cdisplaying Welsh signs in Cornish store
OL,6,FCornish shoppers have been left
OL,7,Fbemused after multiple Welsh language
OL,8,Fsigns appeared at their local Tesco, a
OL,9,Fmistake Cornish language experts have
OL,10,Fbranded "embarrassing."
OL,12,FThe store in Helston mistakenly put up
OL,13,Fbillingual signs directing shoppers to
OL,14,Fgroceries such as "cig a dofednod,"
OL,15,FWelsh for meat and poultry, instead of
OL,16,Fthe Cornish term "kig and yar."
OL,18,FIt also displayed the Welsh signs for
OL,19,Fseafood, sausages and ice cream.
