OL,3,CTesco apologises after accidentally
OL,4,Cdisplaying Welsh signs in Cornish store
OL,6,FSupermarket chain Tesco has since
OL,7,Fapologised for the mistake and says
OL,8,Fthe store has now removed the signage.
OL,10,FShoppers shared their amusement on
OL,11,Fsocial media, some wondering whether
OL,12,FCornish signs had ended up in Wales,
OL,13,Falso.
OL,15,FOne user said: "I like that someone
OL,16,Fsomewhere in their organisation
OL,17,Frealised that bilingual signage was
OL,18,Frelevant here. 10/10 for that! Even if
OL,19,Fthe implementation was a tad lacking."
