OL,3,CTesco apologises after accidentally
OL,4,Cdisplaying Welsh signs in Cornish store
OL,6,FAnother questioned how the mistake
OL,7,Fwent unnoticed.
OL,9,FDr Garry Tregidga, co-director of the
OL,10,FUniversity of Exeter's Institute for
OL,11,FCornish Studies, says while the error
OL,12,Fis "embarrassing," the fact that it
OL,13,Fwas spotted shows signs of an
OL,14,Fincreasing number of people
OL,15,Frecognising the Cornish language.
