OL,3,CTesco apologises after accidentally
OL,4,Cdisplaying Welsh signs in Cornish store
OL,6,FHe said: "This is obviously
OL,7,Fembarrassing for Tesco, but it is
OL,8,Fgreat if there was the intention to
OL,9,Fhave signs in Cornish. I hope there
OL,10,Fwill be replacement signs put up in
OL,11,Fthe right language.
OL,13,F"What is also positive is that this
OL,14,Fmistake was spotted. This is a sign of
OL,15,Fthe increasing number of people who
OL,16,Fare using and recognising Cornish.
OL,18,F"If anyone from Tesco needs assistance
OL,19,Fputting together the new signs there
OL,20,Fare plenty of people who would be glad
OL,21,Fto help."
